            <text>Zoological parks are places where:</text>
            <option id="A">Wild animals are kept in protected environments</option><option id="B">Stuffed animals are kept</option><option id="C">Domestic animals are kept</option><option id="D">Plants are grown</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Zoos.</explanation>
        </question>
        <question>
